						               													<description>Pitch&amp;amp;Plakks is a fun and exciting board game that brings the thrill of miniature golf to your living room. The game features a set of wooden puzzle pieces that can be assembled in countless configurations to create unique and challenging miniature golf courses.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The main objective of the game is to get the ball into the hole with as few kicks as possible. Players must use their finger to hit the ball and avoid obstacles such as tunnels, bridges, jumps or a volcano. The player with the fewest kicks at the end of the game is the winner.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Pitch&amp;amp;Plakks is perfect for players of all ages, and it's easy to learn but difficult to master. The game encourages creativity and strategic thinking, as players must carefully plan their throws and use their skills to overcome obstacles.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;It can be played by 2 to 4 players and is a great way to spend time with friends and family. With its high-quality wooden components and endless customization possibilities, Pitch&amp;amp;Plakks will provide hours of fun and entertainment for players of all ages.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
